## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **rituximab Rituxan 1997** = first FDA anti-CD20 — NHL paradigm 시작. 30년 가까운 lymphoma 임상 standard. quantum-VQE 의 CD20 epitope binding 직접 fit.
2. **CD20xCD3 bispecific 4 (mosunetuzumab 2022 + glofitamab 2023 + epcoritamab 2023 + odronextamab 2024)** = 2022+ paradigm shift "off-the-shelf CAR-T alternative". CRS lower + outpatient 가능 + step-up dosing. quantum-VQE 의 Fab geometry 가 직접 fit.
3. **pola-R-CHP POLARIX 2023** = first new 1L DLBCL in 20+ years. polatuzumab vedotin (anti-CD79b ADC) + R-CHP (CHOP - vincristine). 50+ year R-CHOP backbone 변경의 milestone.
4. **CD19 CAR-T 4 (axi-cel/tisa-cel/brexu-cel/liso-cel) 2017-2021 + 1L 2L 2022 (ZUMA-7 + TRANSFORM)** = LBCL high-risk 1L paradigm shift. 만성 axicabtagene + lisocabtagene 2024 1L 2L 표준. quantum-VQE 직접 fit 한정 (cell therapy).
5. **pirtobrutinib Jaypirca 2023** = first FDA non-covalent BTK — refractory CLL/MCL post-covalent BTKi. C481S mutation 회피. quantum-VQE 의 non-covalent allosteric pocket 결합.
6. **tazemetostat Tazverik 2020** = first EZH2 inhibitor — FL EZH2m + epithelioid sarcoma. 만성 epigenetic methyltransferase 표적. quantum-VQE 의 SET domain pocket leverage.
7. **PI3Kδ inhibitor 4 (idelalisib 2014 + duvelisib 2018 + copanlisib 2017 + umbralisib 2021 → withdrawn 2022)** = PI3Kδ 만성 hepatotoxicity + autoimmune 부작용 problem. umbralisib withdrawal = 안전성 lesson. quantum-VQE selectivity 향상.
8. **loncastuximab tesirine Zynlonta 2021 + polatuzumab vedotin Polivy 2019** = ADC era — anti-CD19 PBD + anti-CD79b MMAE. linker + payload-release 가 quantum-VQE 의 fit.
9. **brentuximab vedotin Adcetris 2011** = anti-CD30 ADC — HL + T-cell. 만성 13 년 임상 standard. PD-1 (nivolumab + pembrolizumab) 와 combo 1L HL 만성.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, lymphoma 임상 의미 한정. 한국 K-lymphoma 식약처 framework 도 wet-lab 없음 한계.

